SELECT
                `MyManufacturer`.id, `MyManufacturer`.preferred_sort, `MyManufacturer`.tcsparts_images, `MyManufacturer`.tcsparts_manufacturer_id, `MyManufacturer`.seo_description, count(`MyProduct`.id) as cnt, `MyManufacturer`.name, `MyImage`.*
            FROM
                my_manufacturers MyManufacturer
            INNER JOIN
                my_products `MyProduct` ON `MyProduct`.manufacturer_id = `MyManufacturer`.id
            LEFT JOIN
                my_images `MyImage` ON (`MyImage`.`ref_id` = `MyManufacturer`.`id` AND `MyImage`.`ref_table` = 'Manufacturer')
            WHERE
                `MyProduct`.`seo_catalog_browsable` = '1' AND  `MyManufacturer`.deleted IS NULL AND `MyProduct`.deleted IS NULL
            GROUP BY
                `MyManufacturer`.name HAVING count(`MyProduct`.id) > 0
            ORDER BY
                `MyManufacturer`.preferred_sort DESC, `MyManufacturer`.seo_popularity DESC, `MyManufacturer`.name ASC
